#: ../../source/language/javascript/scope.rst:2
msgid "作用域与闭包"
msgstr "Scope and Closures"

#: ../../source/language/javascript/scope.rst:5
msgid "作用域与作用域链"
msgstr "Scope and Scope Chains"

#: ../../source/language/javascript/scope.rst:8
msgid "作用域"
msgstr "Scope"

#: ../../source/language/javascript/scope.rst:9
msgid "简单来说，作用域就是变量与函数的可访问范围，即作用域控制着变量与函数的可见性和生命周期。JavaScript的作用域是靠函数来形成的，也就是说一个函数的变量在函数外不可以访问。"
msgstr "In simple terms, scope is the accessibility range of variables and functions. Scope controls the visibility and lifetime of variables and functions. JavaScript scope is formed by functions, which means variables inside a function cannot be accessed outside that function."

#: ../../source/language/javascript/scope.rst:11
msgid "作用域可以分为全局作用域、局部作用域和块级作用域，其中全局作用域主要有以下三种情况："
msgstr "Scope can be divided into global scope, local scope, and block scope. Global scope mainly appears in the following three cases:"

#: ../../source/language/javascript/scope.rst:13
msgid "函数外面定义的变量拥有全局作用域"
msgstr "Variables defined outside functions have global scope."

#: ../../source/language/javascript/scope.rst:14
msgid "未定义直接赋值的变量自动声明为拥有全局作用域"
msgstr "Variables assigned directly without declaration are automatically declared with global scope."

#: ../../source/language/javascript/scope.rst:15
msgid "window对象的属性拥有全局作用"
msgstr "Properties of the window object have global scope."

#: ../../source/language/javascript/scope.rst:17
msgid "局部作用域一般只在固定的代码片段内可访问到，最常见的例如函数内部，所以也会把这种作用域称为函数作用域。"
msgstr "Local scope is generally accessible only within a fixed code segment, most commonly inside a function. Therefore, this kind of scope is also called function scope."

#: ../../source/language/javascript/scope.rst:20
msgid "作用域泄漏"
msgstr "Scope Leakage"

#: ../../source/language/javascript/scope.rst:21
msgid "在ES5标准时，只有全局作用域和局部作用域，没有块级作用域，这样可能会造成变量泄漏的问题。例如："
msgstr "In the ES5 standard, there were only global scope and local scope, with no block scope. This could cause variable leakage. For example:"

#: ../../source/language/javascript/scope.rst:35
msgid "作用域提升（var Hoisting）"
msgstr "Scope Hoisting (var Hoisting)"

#: ../../source/language/javascript/scope.rst:36
msgid "在JavaScript中，使用var在函数或全局内任何地方声明变量相当于在其内部最顶上声明它，这种行为称为Hoisting。例如下面这段代码等效于第二段代码"
msgstr "In JavaScript, declaring a variable with var anywhere inside a function or the global scope is equivalent to declaring it at the top of that scope. This behavior is called hoisting. For example, the following code is equivalent to the second code block."

#: ../../source/language/javascript/scope.rst:58
msgid "作用域链"
msgstr "Scope Chain"

#: ../../source/language/javascript/scope.rst:59
msgid "当函数被执行时，总是先从函数内部找寻局部变量，如果找不到相应的变量，则会向创建函数的上级作用域寻找，直到找到全局作用域为止，这个过程被称为作用域链。"
msgstr "When a function executes, it always looks for local variables inside the function first. If the corresponding variable is not found, it searches the parent scope where the function was created, continuing until it reaches the global scope. This process is called the scope chain."

#: ../../source/language/javascript/scope.rst:62
msgid "闭包"
msgstr "Closures"

#: ../../source/language/javascript/scope.rst:63
msgid ""
"函数与对其状态即词法环境（lexical "
"environment）的引用共同构成闭包（closure）。也就是说，闭包可以让你从内部函数访问外部函数作用域。在JavaScript，函数在每次创建时生成闭包。"
msgstr "A closure is formed by a function together with references to its state, that is, its lexical environment. In other words, a closure lets an inner function access the outer function's scope. In JavaScript, a closure is created every time a function is created."

#: ../../source/language/javascript/scope.rst:65
msgid "在JavaScript中，并没有原生的对private方法的支持，即一个元素/方法只能被同一个类中的其它方法所调用。而闭包则是一种可以被用于模拟私有方法的方案。另外闭包也提供了管理全局命名空间的能力，避免非核心的方法或属性污染了代码的公共接口部分。下面是一个简单的例子："
msgstr "JavaScript has no native support for private methods in the sense that an element or method can be called only by other methods in the same class. Closures provide a way to simulate private methods. Closures also provide a way to manage the global namespace and prevent non-core methods or properties from polluting the public interface of the code. The following is a simple example:"

#: ../../source/language/javascript/scope.rst:95
msgid "全局对象"
msgstr "Global Object"

#: ../../source/language/javascript/scope.rst:96
msgid "全局对象是一个特殊的对象，它的作用域是全局的。"
msgstr "The global object is a special object whose scope is global."

#: ../../source/language/javascript/scope.rst:98
msgid ""
"全平台可用的全局对象是 ``globalThis`` ，它跟全局作用域里的this值相同。另外在浏览器中存在 ``self`` 和 "
"``window`` 全局对象，Web Workers中存在 ``self`` 全局对象，Node.js 中存在 ``global`` 全局对象。"
msgstr "The cross-platform global object is ``globalThis``, which is the same as the this value in global scope. In addition, browsers provide the ``self`` and ``window`` global objects, Web Workers provide the ``self`` global object, and Node.js provides the ``global`` global object."
